Coffee syrup.
You burn a kilo of coffee, you grind it and you do it
puts in a painted earthen pot, pours
above 2 liters of boiling water, it is well diluted with
a spatula, close it hermetically and leave it
for one day in a rather warm place.

After that, it's on to the filter. To every part of this
melting join two of virgin syrup: after
it is placed over a gentle heat and left until it has
reached 32 degrees.
